caption.text: When Lombardi lost his sister his world honestly shattered I remember him not eating or drinking water, laying next to her urn whining, laying on her spot on the couch and not wanting to ever play. I never thought about getting another dog, but Refrigerator sort of showed up and healed Lombardi‚Äôs broken heart. Refrigerator may of not been here for a long time but he sure did save his brother when he came into our lives. #grief #fyp #greatdanes #love #dogvideos
